comments: Hill (MIL) and VanVleet (TOR) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Leonard (TOR) slightly extends his arm into Middleton's (MIL) body prior to his gather, but does not dislodge him as Middleton's momentum is already taking him in that direction.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) wraps Siakam (TOR) during the rebound that affects his ability to get to the loose ball.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Siakam (TOR) and absorbs the contact.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) and Siakam (TOR) engage and disengage as Antetokounmpo (MIL) rolls to the basket after the screen.
Middleton (MIL) initiates contact with Leonard (TOR) during his drive towards the basket and affects his SQBR.
Lopez (MIL) does not establish legal screening position in Powell's (TOR) path and pushes him into Bledsoe (MIL) at the start of his drive.
Bledsoe (MIL) makes marginal contact with VanVleet (TOR) on the perimeter.
Green (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Lopez (MIL) and does not deliver contact.
Middleton (MIL) makes slight body contact with Leonard (TOR) on the perimeter, but does not affect his SQBR.
Leonard (TOR) makes marginal contact with Brogdon (MIL) during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Middleton (MIL) slightly extends his arm into Green's (TOR) body during the inbound, but does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position.
Siakam (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Middleton (MIL) and does not deliver contact.
Bledsoe (MIL) makes slight arm contact with VanVleet (TOR) as he attempts to close out on him on the perimeter, but the contact does not affect VanVleet's SQBR.
[Observable in enhanced video] Antetokounmpo (MIL) lifts his pivot foot after securing the rebound.
RAR shows Gasol (TOR) makes contact to Middleton's (MIL) body after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) commits a take foul on Siakam (TOR).
Middleton (MIL) briefly places his arm around the side of Green (TOR) at the start of his drive towards the basket, but the contact does not affect Green's ability to defend.
Middleton (MIL) and Green (TOR) engage and disengage before the ball is inbounded.
VanVleet (TOR) maintains verticality on Middleton's (MIL) driving shot attempt.
Lopez (MIL) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Siakam (TOR) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Leonard (TOR) briefly brings an arm to Lopez's (MIL) opposite side, but releases as both players move in the same direction.
Gasol (TOR) makes incidental body contact with Antetokounmpo (MIL) as he legally moves alongside Antetokounmpo's body and absorbs the contact during the drive.
Leonard (TOR) makes marginal contact as he is releasing his off-arm from Middleton's (MIL) body at the end of the drive, but doesn't affect his ability to contest the shot attempt.
Lopez (MIL) makes marginal contact with Green (TOR) during the pick on the perimeter.
Siakam (TOR) slightly follows-through with his arm to Brogdon's (MIL) hip, but doesn't affect his SQBR or ability to pass at the end of his drive.
Brogdon (MIL) places his arm to Leonard's (TOR) front at the start of the drive, but the contact is marginal and does not affect Leonard's SQBR or ability to pass.
[Observable in enhanced video] Leonard (TOR) gathers the ball at the end of his drive, leaves his feet, and lands prior to releasing the ball on the pass.
Lopez (MIL) makes marginal contact with Siakam's (TOR) arm after his release, but doesn't affect his ability to follow-through naturally during the driving shot attempt.
Siakam (TOR) makes incidental contact with Brogdon (MIL) after his release and doesn't affect his ability to follow-through naturally during his driving shot attempt.
Leonard (TOR) makes marginal contact with Brogdon (MIL) off-ball, but doesn't affect his ability to maintain defensive position.
[Detectable with a stop watch] Antetokounmpo (MIL) is in the lane for longer than three seconds prior to him imminently actively guarding Gasol (TOR).
Lopez (MIL) slightly extends his arms into Siakam's (TOR) body during the rebound, but the contact does not affect his ability to get to the loose ball.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) grabs Gasol's (TOR) jersey and affects his ability to rebound.
Siakam (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position as he firms up and absorbs the contact from Brogdon (MIL) during the inbound.
RAR shows VanVleet (TOR) makes contact to Hill's (MIL) body prior to gathering the ball during his drive towards the basket. This play should have been whistled as a personal foul.
Gasol (TOR) firms up in Lopez's (MIL) path during the pick and both players briefly engage and separate.
Leonard (TOR) extends his leg as part of a natural shooting motion on the jump shot attempt and the contact with Brogdon (MIL) is marginal.
Brogdon (MIL) makes slight body contact with Leonard (TOR), but does not affect his ability to get to the loose ball.
Lopez (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of VanVleet (TOR) and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Siakam (TOR) makes contact to Brogdon's (MIL) body at the start of the drive but the contact does not affect Brogdon's SQBR.
Siakam (TOR) makes contact to Brogdon's (MIL) body during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Lopez (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Green (TOR) and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Siakam (TOR) jumps from A to B and makes contact to Lopez's (MIL) body and affects his follow through on his shot attempt.
Leonard (TOR) makes contact with Brogdon's (MIL) arm during his driving shot attempt but the contact is marginal.
Lopez (MIL) briefly grasps Gasol's (TOR) arm during the inbound, but does not affect his FOM off-ball.
Lopez (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Siakam (TOR) and absorbs the contact during the pick on the perimeter.
[Observable in enhanced review] Middelton (MIL) lifts his pivot foot on the perimeter.
[Observable in enhanced video] LAR and LLS show Middleton (MIL) releases the ball prior to his foot landing in the backcourt.
Mirotic (MIL) commits a take foul on Siakam (TOR).
Green (TOR) makes marginal contact to Brogdon's (MIL) arm on his driving shot attempt.
Lopez (MIL) commits a take foul on Leonard (TOR).
